Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:22.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:24.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you dropped your notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.47,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The new volume went on sale, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.27,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget all about it, so please don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that one used to curse people you have a grudge against, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my exchange notebook with Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of Tooru's pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are all these names for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A memory test!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're seeing who can write down the most names of people they've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, her memory's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet I couldn't beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, all the names turn foreign-sounding halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Tooru live abroad at one point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting there are characters from manga she's read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that explains the strange names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Justine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh. Michelle Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jule Auguste Gianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-Françoise Victoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovoch Hekenovich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,François Poronac Haque.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel Bomparnasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,O'Brien Vukovich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Alessandro Galexon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Paul Ginades!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Andreas Banderas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Grakios Andretti!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:57.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.36,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Salvadore Andrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.98,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heisel Poncho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.44,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Velázquez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:00.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did Tooru say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had something to show us, so come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never been to Tooru's place before, so I'm pretty excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what kind of place it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the nice apartment she lives in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:39.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, that Tooru. She didn't have to go home early just to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's something she doesn't want you to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like a foot massager! It's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit acting like an old lady and hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:04.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So messy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tooru bad at cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's usually obsessively neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A ransacked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Its owner, missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,And the windows, locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Except the front entrance was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't just being a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look. The trash in the trash bin just got scattered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the trash went for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they have legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! A human is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It all makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, should we clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's what you were thinking, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's so messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This little guy was tearing up the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked him up this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:39.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Cats have legs too, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you mean, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat could be personified, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I bet it'd be Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,... I think I could live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say bye to the kitty for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten colder. You okay, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to grab something to eat on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'd like something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we could go to a family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head through the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shopping district, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, can we stop by somewhere on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember, it was somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy a collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, some cat toys, and various other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I know a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll sell them here, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll sell them, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a huge problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A white cat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what color would look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red? Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at how serious she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really care for that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really care for you, too, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to G-N's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, you can have the sofa seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have it, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's just sit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,About my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never decide at the drink bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How many flavors are you putting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Five-delicious-flavors-at-once mixed juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you haven't decided on the cat's name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come up with a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not name it after a sweet or a juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What I've got here right now are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:17.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,cola, cider, ramune, ginger ale, and melon soda, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,putting them all together, you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Carbonation"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, you'll be named "Carbonation"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very well-behaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs wild now and then, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonation, that collar looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:44.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll feed you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we got you some toys, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's play after you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ended up not getting any attention from Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Carbonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad boy. You'll get fur on my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Temperatures will be very low this morning, continuing throughout the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance of snow this afternoon is high,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so please be prepared as you leave home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten even colder today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's going to snow today, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, according to the forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:15.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought syrup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,For the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another cold morning today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morn{\fscx200}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi! What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:01.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The forecast said snow, so I made suitable preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like an assassin! How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:13.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to come to school in this blasted cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural. We're students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they should make it winter break from the end of fall to the start of spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must hate winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite constantly ranting about how hot summer was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,When the snow comes falling, I just lose the will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the depressing talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowy days are full of fun things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like making snowmen, or making igloos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,or having snowball fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:46.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you should pray for snow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:54.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even listen to a single thing I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't given up yet, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've half given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just completely give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's started snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.16,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}It's the first snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather changes on a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, isn't that wonderf{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:43.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.46,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Eat your bento, not snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it'll pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If a lot piles up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get buried so deep, you can't see the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I jumped from here, I bet I could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:24.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then what about from the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It piled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's eating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's all jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, don't do that so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, that's a funny pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,quite warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:01.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, we'll warm you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making an igloo for Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear those are warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, feeling warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, better than outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open, Yuuko-chan! Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,After playing around so much outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised I didn't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"I caught a cold. -Yuuko"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you catch one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've got a fever of 38 degrees. -Tooru"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looks like I've caught a cold. -Run"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:36.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:40.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:48.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shovel with all we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:50.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do last winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:24:01.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka was tutoring you for high school entrance exams, Miporin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:03.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on A-Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:04.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Birthday"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, good luck with your exam studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what month it is now?
